        <abstract> 
<p>Advises JVC on how his publisher might deal with problem of getting satisfactory heliotype copies for 2d [German] edition of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Regrets that he will again be away in August, when JVC might have come for a visit.</p>
